basics.name: Taylor Alison Swift
basics.label: UI/UX Designer, Frontend Developer
basics.summary: A detail-oriented and motivated Information Technology graduate with a strong interest in web development and software design. Skilled in using modern tools and technologies to create efficient, user-centered digital solutions. Eager to apply technical knowledge, creativity, and collaboration skills to contribute to innovative projects and continuous learning in the tech sector.

work.name: UX/UI Designer
work.summary: Designed and improved user interfaces for web and mobile applications. Collaborated with developers and stakeholders to create visually appealing and user-friendly designs. Conducted user research, built wireframes and prototypes, and ensured consistent user experiences across all platforms.
highlights: Conducted user research to understand user needs and pain points.
Created wireframes, prototypes, and visual mockups using Figma and other design tools.
Collaborated with developers to ensure accurate design implementation.

advisory.organization: Fund the Arts Organization, University of California
